title: I AM ATHLETE | MICHAEL STRAHAN: Mastering Life After Football
description:
SUBSCRIBE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE?sub_confirmation=1
WATCH MORE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE

Michael Strahan joins Brandon Marshall, Adam "Pacman" Jones, and LeSean "Shady" McCoy and in episode 50 of I Am Athlete. Watch this episode as the hall of fame pass rusher Michael discusses how he used his playing career to help become a pioneer in the media landscape. Listen as the Good Morning America host addressed all the obstacles he’s had to overcome to be the trendsetter he is today.
